Alcarin, Warrior of Lamedon<br />
Turgon, Man of Belfalas<br />
<br />
Site Path:<br />
1.	Western Wmyn Muil (Anti Ring Bound)<br />
2.	Rohirrim Village (No Archery VS your Dunland Men)<br />
3.	Westernment Plains (No Archery VS your Dunland Men Again!)<br />
4.	White Rocks (Good against Rohan Mount decks)<br />
5.	Deeping Wall (Grab Saruman from Library)<br />
6.	Hornburg <a href="javascript:card_browser(303)">Armor</a>y (I have a few possessions)<br />
7.	Hornburn Causeway (anti large fellowships)<br />
8.	Ring of Isengard (Card Drawing Advantage)<br />
9.	Orthanc Balcony (Grab Saruman from Discard Pile at &#8211;2 cost)<br />
<br />
Free Peoples (37):<br />
1x <a href="javascript:card_browser(5)">Foes of Mordor</a><br />
